RivalsHouse_1F_Text_OhYoureTheNewNeighbor:
	.string "Oh, a child wandered into my house.\n"
	.string "That's normal here. No locks.\p"
	.string "You must be {PLAYER}{KUN}, the new\n"
	.string "neighbor! Welcome to LITTLEROOT!\p"
	.string "We have a {STR_VAR_1} your age. They're\n"
	.string "upstairs. Doing POKéMON things.\p"
	.string "They're ALWAYS doing POKéMON things.$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_LikeChildLikeFather:
	.string "My husband and my child are identical.\n"
	.string "Both obsessed with POKéMON.\p"
	.string "Neither of them is ever home.\n"
	.string "I live alone with a ZIGZAGOON.\l"
	.string "The ZIGZAGOON is better company.$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_TooBusyToNoticeVisit:
	.string "That {RIVAL}!\p"
	.string "I guess our child is too busy with\n"
	.string "POKéMON to notice that you came\l"
	.string "to visit, {PLAYER}{KUN}.$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_WentOutToRoute103:
	.string "Oh, {RIVAL} went out to ROUTE 103\n"
	.string "just a little while ago.\p"
	.string "Like father, like child.\n"
	.string "{RIVAL} can't stay quietly at home.$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_ShouldGoHomeEverySoOften:
	.string "Visit your mother sometimes, okay?\p"
	.string "She's sitting alone in that house\n"
	.string "while you and your father are both\l"
	.string "out living your best lives.\p"
	.string "I know because I'm doing the same\n"
	.string "thing. We should start a club.$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_MayWhoAreYou:
	.string "WHO ARE YOU AND WHY ARE YOU IN MY\n"
	.string "ROOM?!\p"
	.string "… … … … … … … …\n"
	.string "… … … … … … … …\p"
	.string "Oh, you're {PLAYER}{KUN}. The new kid.\n"
	.string "My mom just let you walk upstairs, huh?\p"
	.string "I'm MAY. My dream is to befriend\n"
	.string "every POKéMON in existence.\p"
	.string "People say that's 'unrealistic' and\n"
	.string "'a sign of concerning ambition' but\l"
	.string "I think they're just jealous.\p"
	.string "My dad told me about you. He said\n"
	.string "you'd be 'interesting.' Which is\l"
	.string "professor-speak for 'useful.'\p"
	.string "OH WAIT. I was supposed to go help\n"
	.string "my dad catch wild POKéMON. For free.\l"
	.string "Again. Later, {PLAYER}{KUN}!$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_BrendanWhoAreYou:
	.string "Yo! How did you get in here?!\p"
	.string "Oh wait. Nobody locks their doors in\n"
	.string "this town. My bad.\p"
	.string "You're {PLAYER}, right? GYM LEADER's\n"
	.string "kid? My dad wouldn't shut up about you.\p"
	.string "I'm BRENDAN. I've been doing POKéMON\n"
	.string "research since before I could read.\l"
	.string "Which is still, technically, now.\p"
	.string "You don't have a POKéMON? Seriously?\n"
	.string "That's like not having SHOES.\p"
	.string "I'd catch you one but I gotta go help\n"
	.string "my dad do his job. For no pay.\l"
	.string "The grind never stops. Later!$"

RivalsHouse_1F_Text_DoYouHavePokemon:
	.string "Hi, neighbor!\p"
	.string "Do you already have your\n"
	.string "own POKéMON?$"
